Wasn't her name "Zoe"? And thanx for reminding me about Slayer, I'd
forgotten.

::Slayer::

Slayer looks ahead, seeing the Cybertronian Fire a few miles off. He
smiles, taking out his missile launcher. He walks forward untill he
was in range of the ship.

"We're here. Lets fire a few shots, hopefully they'll follow us."

He aims the missile launcher at the CF, firing two missiles.

"I've engaged the Maximals," he says over his comm to Ignatius as the
missiles fly.
